slave_world_description:
[Helen]
- My world is ruled by giant multinational corporations. Territorial governments have lost their power and do what the oligarchs dictate. It is difficult to find a good job, but those who work for corporations can rely on good earnings.
slave_family_description:
[Helen]
- My father was the manager of recruitment in Dynamical Pharmaceuticals, and my mother worked as a math tutor for rich kids. With the support of my parents, I managed to get a good education and a career in the company where my dad worked.
slave_occupation_description:
[Helen]
- Then I met Greg - he was a line manager at Vega Industries and had good prospects for his career. We got married and I quit my job to become a housewife, gave birth to a son. But then Greg fucked up and he was expelled from the service. Because of debts we were deprived of civil rights and became the property of the bank.
